                </svg>
                <span class="yyz-visually-hidden">Opens in a new tab</span>
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Connect with HR leaders from prominent Toronto-area organizations to learn, share ideas, and support one-another.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-list-label">People &amp; Culture Council Events Always Include:</p>
        <ul class="hero-list">
          <li>Topical Group Discussion</li>
          <li>Networking</li>
          <li>Food &amp; Refreshments</li>
          <li>Fun Experiences</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="hero-secondary-actions">
          <p class="hero-pricing-note">Have questions? <a href="mailto:garrett.genest@kudos.com">Get in touch here.</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-card" id="top-form">
